Uses of Interface
ch.bfh.ti.ostes2.gossip.Message

    • Uses of Message in ch.bfh.ti.ostes2.gossip

      Classes in ch.bfh.ti.ostes2.gossip that implement Message 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  ActionMessage
      This class acts as container for messages used either to perform updates from a Frontend to a ReplicationManager or for a ReplicationManager to answer a request from a Frontend.
      class  GossipMessage
      This class acts as container for messages used to send gossip messages between ReplicationManagers.
      class  QueryMessage
      This class acts as container for query messages between a Frontend and a ReplicationManager.
      Methods in ch.bfh.ti.ostes2.gossip that return Message 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Message LogRecord.getMessage()
      Returns the Message of the LogRecord which can be either an ActionMessage, a QueryMessage or a GossipMessage.

      Modifier and Type Method and Description

      Sets the Message of the LogRecord.
